{"tid":881494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"勇士外，James隊波係咪近四年最強隊伍？","createTime":"2018-10-29T13:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T17:49:29.000Z","uid":113326,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"90d77c77d0221250c0707566c71f0b9a339b9053","tid":881494,"uid":113326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"1516兩年間，只有雷霆騎士能夠同冇kd勇士搶7。<br />\n其中，雷霆有被黑哨疑雲；騎士有黑哨疑雲<br />\n<br />\n簡言之，雷霆、勇士、騎士三隊實力大約在同一層次，先不細分排名（先忽略curry季後賽受傷）<br />\n<br />\n17勇士有kd加盟，而16騎士同16勇士搶7，而17年騎士陣容、磨合程度，亦較16騎士強，但在近乎公認黑哨下，仍1-4落敗。可見，17勇士比16勇士更高一層次。<br />\n<br />\n18勇士陣容沒有大變，磨合更好情況下，卻與火箭搶7。至於1718騎士就亦唔能夠對勇士構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n近兩年，火箭唯一一隊，能與進化的勇士搶7。可見，18火箭&gt;17騎士。而17 騎士又係4年間最強騎士型態。"},{"pid":"22628486deafe13cd8f056513e61052db002b752","tid":881494,"uid":15948,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"19999999999"},{"pid":"94e088cdb94c8329e83a2aa86458625b9c987d2c","tid":881494,"uid":23200,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"你洗唔洗睇醫生 有第三期語癌"},{"pid":"8afe759dcdc8b2281b7936be2fc7fe43ea2de472","tid":881494,"uid":72621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"2014刺"},{"pid":"f8bf1c438876efd37f5fb48a7c242b34be8c825d","tid":881494,"uid":1790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"哇 你唔講我真係唔知"},{"pid":"588d2228a94284adb526e9d5b388da40fa171a11","tid":881494,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"1920湖人 <br />\nBall klay lbj kuzma ingram"},{"pid":"4d78bfb70de75fb2532368e14a66a5f8a2fc3907","tid":881494,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"588d2228a94284adb526e9d5b388da40fa171a11","tid":881494,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"1920湖人 <br />\nBall klay lbj kuzma ingram"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:09:47.